VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \beval\(.+\)
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:(input\(|request|params|query|user_input|base64|pickle) && MISSING:(allowlist|whitelist)
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects the usage of eval() function, which can lead to arbitrary code execution vulnerabilities.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Arbitrary Code Execution: eval().
